<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Crockett</ENAMEX> said the program, funded by a <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$300,000</NUMEX> grant from the
<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">U.S.</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Justice Department</ENAMEX>, has no economic restrictions on who can
