<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Gladys Bunzy</ENAMEX>, who said she was in an abusive relationship with a
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">boyfriend</ENAMEX> for <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">eight years</TIMEX>, said such a program is long overdue and
