"When I finally made up my mind to leave, I had a restraining
order put against him and that was <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$50</NUMEX> but that was <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$50 well</NUMEX> spent
to me," said <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Bunzy</ENAMEX>, <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">40</TIMEX>. "For <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">people</ENAMEX> who can't afford it, this will
be a godsend ... If a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">woman</ENAMEX> knows she is going to get some help
