that <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">person</ENAMEX> away from her."
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Gwen Bouie-Haynes</ENAMEX>, project <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">director</ENAMEX> of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Domestic Violence</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Services Center for Catholic Charities Inc.</ENAMEX>, said often domestic
