<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Lark Johnson</ENAMEX>, executive <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">director</ENAMEX> at the shelter, said some of
the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">women</ENAMEX> would never have received legal help had it not been for
