<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Johnson</ENAMEX> said through the program her <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">shelter</ENAMEX>, which served <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">187</NUMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">women</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">children</ENAMEX> <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">last year</TIMEX>, has been able to form better
relationships with those who work with domestic violence
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">victims</ENAMEX>.
"<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Judges</ENAMEX> and law enforcement <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">officers</ENAMEX> are trained to help them
