Educating <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">court</ENAMEX> and law enforcement <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">officers</ENAMEX> is a program
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">priority</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Crockett</ENAMEX> said, because in that emotional and painful
